                            <comment id="229698" author="jamesanunez" created="Fri, 22 Jun 2018 18:52:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;recovery-small test 60 was removed from the ALWAYS_EXCEPT list in the patch for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9624&quot; title=&quot;enable sanity.sh test_160a failures for DNE&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-9624&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-9624&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; with commit a37134d398801c10922c32eb03c52b2d46bb6c18; &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/27535/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/27535/&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll modify the patch for this ticket to remove test 52 and see if we trigger &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9808&quot; title=&quot;recovery-small test 102: osd_destroy()) ASSERTION( !lu_object_is_dying(dt-&amp;gt;do_lu.lo_header) ) failed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-9808&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-9808&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="204530" author="jamesanunez" created="Fri, 4 Aug 2017 21:49:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;When these tests are removed from the ALWAYS_EXCEPT list and run with the rest of the test suite, tests 101 and 102 crash all the time in some test environments, gatekeeper&apos;s for one, with this assertion:&lt;br/&gt;
osd_destroy()) ASSERTION( !lu_object_is_dying(dt-&amp;gt;do_lu.lo_header) ) failed&lt;/p&gt;

